🌐 My Portfolio Webpage

Welcome to my personal portfolio website — a digital space that reflects my journey as a Software Engineer and Web Developer. This site encapsulates my technical expertise, creative projects, and passion for crafting elegant, efficient, and user-centric software solutions.

---------------------------------------------

👩‍💻 About Me

I’m Yatharth Rahangdale, a Bachelor of Engineering (Computer Science & Engineering) student with a strong academic background and a deep enthusiasm for technology-driven innovation. I’m passionate about transforming ideas into tangible, real-world applications that solve problems and deliver meaningful impact. My focus lies in developing scalable, responsive, and performance-optimized web applications using modern tools and technologies.

---------------------------------------------

⚙️ Key Features

⦁	Fully Responsive Design — Optimized for seamless viewing across all devices.
⦁	Project Showcase — Highlighting my most impactful academic and personal projects.
⦁	Technical Skills Overview — A concise display of my programming and development proficiencies.
